# Gmail SMTP Configuration for Contact Form
# =============================================
#
# 1. Use a Gmail account (or create one for this purpose)
# 2. Enable 2-Step Verification on the Gmail account:
#    https://myaccount.google.com/security
# 3. Generate an App Password:
#    https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#    - Select "Mail" as the app
#    - Select "Other" as the device, name it "ETIM Pro Website"
#    - Copy the 16-character password
#
# Then rename this file to .env.local and fill in the values below:

GMAIL_USER=your-gmail@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=your-16-char-app-password
